## Visualization notes\
\
To keep plots stable:\
\
\'95 Histogram display is clipped to a fixed window  \
\'95 Tail mass outside the window is reported  \
\'95 KS distance is computed from the unclipped data  \
\
This preserves statistical correctness while maintaining readable visuals.\
